		    @{b}WinCommodity@{ub} ©1996 by @{"Michael Gollmick" LINK Author}

This documentation describes the program @{b}WinCommodity@{ub}, the useful
utility for the dayly work with your Amiga.
@{b}WinCommodity@{ub} requires at least version 2.04 of the AmigaOS.

- GENERAL -
